metadata.name: 3D Bored Ape Can [#1/1]
metadata.description:
The world of crypto is nothing but amazing. 3D Ape is a pop culture construction around the Apes. Artist OrionDeimos has created a 3d CAN of this ape. Object that brings the image of the crypto space to life and allows you to enjoy it every day.
Limited edition, original creation.


Creator : OrionDeimos
Music : Lexin Music
Unique Edition 1/1
